data.description: Luxury at its best. Move to this beautifully designed, both inside and out, 2½ year old home with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. This lovely home has vaulted decorative ceilings, quartz countertops, wood look 'easy care' tile floors. The home is light and bright with big windows. AND, you will love the kitchen layout with the breakfast bar/work station. The kitchen cabinets are plentiful, and quality built. The homeowners are leaving the stove and refrigerator that complement the kitchen design. The utility room is conveniently located near the kitchen. The main suite has a wonderful bath with farmhouse sinks, its spacious shower is built with frameless glass and the main suite closet has built in shelving and drawers. And oh my, what a wonderful big backyard! Great for entertaining and family gatherings.
